title: Additional Public Sector Schemes, Afghanistan, UNOPS, 2001
name: Additional Public Sector Schemes, Afghanistan, UNOPS, 2001
description:
This data shows additional public sector irrigation schemes in Afghanistan. Data is from the UNOPS from 2001 and includes approximate irrigated area and approximate electricity generated for each scheme by province. Some provinces have multiple schemes separated by a comma. 

Uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
